l.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDV/110%2c%e5%8f%b8%e6%b6%88%e5%82%b5%e8%81%b2%2c3%2c20210729%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDV,110,司消債聲,3,20210729,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"司消債聲","JNO":"3","JDATE":"20210729","JTITLE":"聲請延長履行期限"}